{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000",
   "children": [],
   "end": "1.680",
   "id": "span0",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "In the evenings, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "1.680",
   "children": [],
   "end": "4.920",
   "id": "span1",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "after he had finished his supper of watery cabbage soup, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "4.920",
   "children": [],
   "end": "10.520",
   "id": "span2",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "Charlie always went into the room of his four grandparents to listen to\n\n        their stories, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "10.520",
   "children": [],
   "end": "12.960",
   "id": "span3",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "and then afterwards to say good night.\n\n      "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "12.960",
   "children": [],
   "end": "16.040",
   "id": "span4",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "Every one of these old people was over ninety. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "16.040",
   "children": [],
   "end": "17.360",
   "id": "span5",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "They were as shrivelled as prunes, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "17.360",
   "children": [],
   "end": "18.040",
   "id": "span6",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "and as bony as skeletons, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "18.040",
   "children": [],
   "end": "18.600",
   "id": "span7",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "and throughout the day, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "18.600",
   "children": [],
   "end": "18.920",
   "id": "span8",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "until Charlie made his appearance, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "18.920",
   "children": [],
   "end": "20.840",
   "id": "span9",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "they lay huddled in their one bed, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "20.840",
   "children": [],
   "end": "22.080",
   "id": "span10",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "two at either end, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "22.080",
   "children": [],
   "end": "24.720",
   "id": "span11",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "with nightcaps on to keep their heads warm, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "24.720",
   "children": [],
   "end": "27.920",
   "id": "span12",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "dozing the time away with nothing to do. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "27.920",
   "children": [],
   "end": "30.080",
   "id": "span13",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "But as soon as they heard the door opening, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "30.080",
   "children": [],
   "end": "31.560",
   "id": "span14",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "and heard Charlie\u2019s voice saying, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "31.560",
   "children": [],
   "end": "32.360",
   "id": "span15",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018Good evening, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "32.360",
   "children": [],
   "end": "34.480",
   "id": "span16",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "Grandpa Joe and Grandma Josephine, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "34.480",
   "children": [],
   "end": "39.480",
   "id": "span17",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "and Grandpa George and Grandma Georgina,\u2019 then all four of them would\n\n        suddenly sit up, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "39.480",
   "children": [],
   "end": "45.520",
   "id": "span18",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "and their old wrinkled faces would light up with smiles of pleasure \u2013\n\n        and the talking would begin. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "45.520",
   "children": [],
   "end": "47.680",
   "id": "span19",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "For they loved this little boy. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "47.680",
   "children": [],
   "end": "48.560",
   "id": "span20",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "He was the only bright thing in their lives, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "48.560",
   "children": [],
   "end": "50.760",
   "id": "span21",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "and his evening visits were something that they looked forward to all\n\n        day long. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "50.760",
   "children": [],
   "end": "51.120",
   "id": "span22",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "Often, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "51.120",
   "children": [],
   "end": "53.920",
   "id": "span23",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "Charlie\u2019s mother and father would come in as well, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "53.920",
   "children": [],
   "end": "55.520",
   "id": "span24",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "and stand by the door, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "55.520",
   "children": [],
   "end": "59.480",
   "id": "span25",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "listening to the stories that the old people told; and thus, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "59.480",
   "children": [],
   "end": "61.720",
   "id": "span26",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "for perhaps half an hour every night, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "61.720",
   "children": [],
   "end": "63.160",
   "id": "span27",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "this room would become a happy place, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "63.160",
   "children": [],
   "end": "65.200",
   "id": "span28",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "and the whole family would forget that it was hungry and poor.\n\n      "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "65.200",
   "children": [],
   "end": "66.160",
   "id": "span29",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "One evening, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "66.160",
   "children": [],
   "end": "68.280",
   "id": "span30",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "when Charlie went in to see his grandparents, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "68.280",
   "children": [],
   "end": "68.840",
   "id": "span31",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "he said to them, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "68.840",
   "children": [],
   "end": "73.480",
   "id": "span32",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018Is it really true that Wonka\u2019s Chocolate Factory is the biggest in the\n\n        world?\u2019\n\n      "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "73.480",
   "children": [],
   "end": "76.600",
   "id": "span33",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018True?\u2019 cried all four of them at once. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "76.600",
   "children": [],
   "end": "78.160",
   "id": "span34",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018Of course it\u2019s true! "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "78.160",
   "children": [],
   "end": "78.800",
   "id": "span35",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "Good heavens, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "78.800",
   "children": [],
   "end": "79.080",
   "id": "span36",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "didn\u2019t you know that? "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "79.080",
   "children": [],
   "end": "80.600",
   "id": "span37",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "It\u2019s about fifty times as big as any other!\u2019\n\n      "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "80.600",
   "children": [],
   "end": "86.400",
   "id": "span38",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018And is Mr Willy Wonka really the cleverest chocolate maker in the\n\n        world?\u2019\n\n      "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "86.400",
   "children": [],
   "end": "88.720",
   "id": "span39",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018My dear boy,\u2019 said Grandpa Joe, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "88.720",
   "children": [],
   "end": "90.840",
   "id": "span40",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "raising himself up a little higher on his pillow, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "90.840",
   "children": [],
   "end": "93.640",
   "id": "span41",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018Mr Willy Wonka is the most amazing, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "93.640",
   "children": [],
   "end": "94.240",
   "id": "span42",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "the most fantastic, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "94.240",
   "children": [],
   "end": "96.480",
   "id": "span43",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "the most extraordinary chocolate maker the world has ever seen! "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "96.480",
   "children": [],
   "end": "97.280",
   "id": "span44",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "I thought everybody knew that!\u2019 "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "97.280",
   "children": [],
   "end": "97.680",
   "id": "span45",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018I knew he was famous, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "97.680",
   "children": [],
   "end": "98.040",
   "id": "span46",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "Grandpa Joe, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "98.040",
   "children": [],
   "end": "98.560",
   "id": "span47",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "and I knew he was very clever\u2026\u2019 "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "98.560",
   "children": [],
   "end": "99.080",
   "id": "span48",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018Clever!\u2019 cried the old man. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "99.080",
   "children": [],
   "end": "99.880",
   "id": "span49",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018He\u2019s more than that! "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "99.880",
   "children": [],
   "end": "101.000",
   "id": "span50",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "He\u2019s a magician with chocolate! "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "101.000",
   "children": [],
   "end": "104.040",
   "id": "span51",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "He can make anything \u2013 anything he wants! "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "104.040",
   "children": [],
   "end": "104.720",
   "id": "span52",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "Isn\u2019t that a fact, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "104.720",
   "children": [],
   "end": "105.920",
   "id": "span53",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "my dears?\u2019 "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "105.920",
   "children": [],
   "end": "108.720",
   "id": "span54",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "The other three old people nodded their heads slowly up and down, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "108.720",
   "children": [],
   "end": "109.400",
   "id": "span55",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "and said, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "109.400",
   "children": [],
   "end": "110.400",
   "id": "span56",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018Absolutely true. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "110.400",
   "children": [],
   "end": "111.000",
   "id": "span57",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "Just as true as can be.\u2019 "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "111.000",
   "children": [],
   "end": "111.360",
   "id": "span58",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "And Grandpa Joe said, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "111.360",
   "children": [],
   "end": "114.280",
   "id": "span59",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018You mean to say I\u2019ve never told you about Mr Willy Wonka and his\n\n        factory?\u2019\n\n      "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "114.280",
   "children": [],
   "end": "116.560",
   "id": "span60",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018Never,\u2019 answered little Charlie. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "116.560",
   "children": [],
   "end": "117.440",
   "id": "span61",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018Good heavens above! "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "117.440",
   "children": [],
   "end": "118.360",
   "id": "span62",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "I don\u2019t know what\u2019s the matter with me!\u2019\n\n      "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "118.360",
   "children": [],
   "end": "119.960",
   "id": "span63",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018Will you tell me now, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "119.960",
   "children": [],
   "end": "120.640",
   "id": "span64",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "Grandpa Joe, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "120.640",
   "children": [],
   "end": "121.040",
   "id": "span65",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "please?\u2019 "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "121.040",
   "children": [],
   "end": "122.680",
   "id": "span66",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018I certainly will. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "122.680",
   "children": [],
   "end": "124.040",
   "id": "span67",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "Sit down beside me on the bed, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "124.040",
   "children": [],
   "end": "124.600",
   "id": "span68",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "my dear, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "124.600",
   "children": [],
   "end": "126.960",
   "id": "span69",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "and listen carefully.\u2019 "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "126.960",
   "children": [],
   "end": "130.240",
   "id": "span70",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "Grandpa Joe was the oldest of the four grandparents. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "130.240",
   "children": [],
   "end": "132.280",
   "id": "span71",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "He was ninety-six and a half, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "132.280",
   "children": [],
   "end": "135.680",
   "id": "span72",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "and that is just about as old as anybody can be. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "135.680",
   "children": [],
   "end": "137.760",
   "id": "span73",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "Like all extremely old people, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "137.760",
   "children": [],
   "end": "139.640",
   "id": "span74",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "he was delicate and weak, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "139.640",
   "children": [],
   "end": "141.680",
   "id": "span75",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "and throughout the day he spoke very little. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "141.680",
   "children": [],
   "end": "143.680",
   "id": "span76",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "But in the evenings, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "143.680",
   "children": [],
   "end": "144.320",
   "id": "span77",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "when Charlie, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "144.320",
   "children": [],
   "end": "145.440",
   "id": "span78",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "his beloved grandson, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "145.440",
   "children": [],
   "end": "146.080",
   "id": "span79",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "was in the room, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "146.080",
   "children": [],
   "end": "150.760",
   "id": "span80",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "he seemed in some marvellous way to grow quite young again. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "150.760",
   "children": [],
   "end": "152.880",
   "id": "span81",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "All his tiredness fell away from him, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "152.880",
   "children": [],
   "end": "155.920",
   "id": "span82",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "and he became as eager and excited as a young boy.\n\n      "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "155.920",
   "children": [],
   "end": "157.320",
   "id": "span83",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018Oh, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "157.320",
   "children": [],
   "end": "158.480",
   "id": "span84",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "what a man he is, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "158.480",
   "children": [],
   "end": "160.920",
   "id": "span85",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "this Mr Willy Wonka!\u2019 cried Grandpa Joe. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "160.920",
   "children": [],
   "end": "162.080",
   "id": "span86",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018Did you know, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "162.080",
   "children": [],
   "end": "163.080",
   "id": "span87",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "for example, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "163.080",
   "children": [],
   "end": "167.320",
   "id": "span88",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "that he has himself invented more than two hundred new kinds of\n\n        chocolate bars, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "167.320",
   "children": [],
   "end": "169.200",
   "id": "span89",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "each with a different centre, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "169.200",
   "children": [],
   "end": "174.880",
   "id": "span90",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "each far sweeter and creamier and more delicious than anything the\n\n        other chocolate factories can make!\u2019\n\n      "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "174.880",
   "children": [],
   "end": "178.400",
   "id": "span91",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018Perfectly true!\u2019 cried Grandma Josephine. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "178.400",
   "children": [],
   "end": "181.600",
   "id": "span92",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018And he sends them to all the four corners of the earth! "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "181.600",
   "children": [],
   "end": "182.360",
   "id": "span93",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "Isn\u2019t that so, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "182.360",
   "children": [],
   "end": "183.160",
   "id": "span94",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "Grandpa Joe?\u2019 "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "183.160",
   "children": [],
   "end": "184.280",
   "id": "span95",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "\u2018It is, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "184.280",
   "children": [],
   "end": "184.480",
   "id": "span96",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "my dear, "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "184.480",
   "children": [],
   "end": "185.080",
   "id": "span97",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "it is. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "185.080",
   "children": [],
   "end": "185.840",
   "id": "span98",
   "language": "eng",
   "lines": [
    "And to all the kings and presidents of the world as well. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "185.840",
